items.headline: When Captain America throws his mighty shield...
items.desc:
'''Captain America''' is a Marvel Comics superhero who, in most versions, is frail Steve Rogers, who volunteers for a World War 2 Super-Soldier experiment. After many adventures, he (through different means from version to version, but mostly by being frozen) ends in the present day where he becomes the leader of the Avengers and the moral compass of the Marvel Universe.

This is a wiki about Captain America, his allies, foes, and fictional appearances like comic books, TV series, movies, videogames, etc.
